org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT spree_variants.* FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_prices ON spree_prices.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.variant_id = spree_variants.id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND (spree_variants.discontinue_on IS NULL OR spree_variants.discontinue_on >= '2022-08-14 05:34:49.885916') AND spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.currency = 'USD' AND spree_prices.amount IS NOT NULL AND spree_variants.sku = "$1" LIMIT "$2"
